<section class="pricing section">
  <div class="container text-column">
    <h2 class="pricing__headline" data-fade>One number. Agreed before we start.</h2>
    <p class="pricing__body" data-fade style="--fade-delay:80ms">
      Every Echo 7 engagement is a fixed fee, agreed in full before work begins.
      No hourly billing. No scope creep clauses. No commercial reason for us to slow down.
      The diagnostic is a fixed fee. The transformation is a fixed fee. The retainer is
      a fixed annual figure. We do not publish a rate card because your estate is not a
      list item — but we will commit the number in writing before you commit to anything.
    </p>
    <p class="pricing__kicker" data-fade style="--fade-delay:120ms">
      If a provider can't tell you what something costs before they start, ask yourself
      who that uncertainty serves.
    </p>
    <a href="/contact" class="link-subtle" data-fade style="--fade-delay:160ms">
      Ask us the number →
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pricing__headline {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
  }

  .pricing__body {
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    color: var(--colour-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .pricing__kicker {
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--colour-text);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .pricing a.link-subtle {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }
</style>
